<div style="text-align: center;">
<p>凡人终死竞赛第一轮参赛作品</p>
</div>
<br />
<strong>本轮角色</strong>：Consolas Lake<br />
<strong>基准文档</strong>：<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/project-proposal-2024-239">项目建议书 2024-239：“加冕仪式”</a>；<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/project-proposal-2014-2390">项目建议书 2014-2390：“Mr.Sue”</a><br />
<strong>本轮对手</strong>：<a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/homunculus">霍尔蒙克斯</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/reverberate-a" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255954); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5255954&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569472" alt="Reverberate_a" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5255954)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/reverberate-a" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5255954); return false;">Reverberate_a</a></span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/danza" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5206218); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5206218&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569472" alt="Danza" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5206218)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/danza" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5206218); return false;">Danza</a></span><br />
或 <a href="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/scp-cn-930">SCP-CN-930</a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3967806&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569472" alt="ShineShadowD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3967806)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/shineshadowd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3967806); return false;">ShineShadowD</a></span> &amp; <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ghostlin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5037208); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5037208&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1600569472" alt="ghostlin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5037208)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ghostlin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5037208); return false;">ghostlin</a></span><br />
